This file contains information about this directory.

==========
lab1a.c
==========
Usage: ./lab1a [OPTION]...
put the keyboard (the file open on file descriptor 0)
into character-at-a-time, no-echo mode
(also known as non-canonical input mode with no echo)

  --shell  pass input/output between the terminal and a shell
  --debug  run program in debug mode

==========
Makefile
==========
default:   create executable
clean:     clean up files generated by `make` or `make dist`
dist:      create tarball for distribution

